General.Name: DomaCom Limited
General.Description: DomaCom Limited, through its subsidiaries, develops a software platform for trading of fractional interests in properties in Australia. The company manages DomaCom Fund, an investment scheme that allows investors to hold fractional interests in underlying assets. It also engages in the sales and marketing of fractionalized asset products; and administration of the senior equity release products, as well as provision of investment management services. In addition, it operates as a trustee for DomaCom Rental Property Accelerator trusts; and trustee for DomaCom Loan Fund. The company was formerly known as DomaCom Holdings Limited and changed its name into DomaCom Limited in March 2015. DomaCom Limited was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
